<br />
<span style="font-weight: bold">CC major, </span>the old school lock em down school
<br />

<br />
<span style="font-weight: bold">Nuke / buff bot major</span> Basically what we are at the moment
<br />

<br />
How would it get done. Many thoughts but the major requirement is for SOE to engage with the chanter community and not look at the dissenters as evidence there is no consensus but realise that the chanter class is not homogenous. Of course not listening to the chattering classes biatching and moaning would assist.</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
